      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAWRENNY BOYS (2) has placed last five runs and deserves to break through. On speed and fought on well again last time here over 1200m. Small field suits and expected to take catching. CAN'T CATCH CHILLI (6) was placed fresh then ran below par last time when a weakened ninth. Was gassed early though from an outside gate to go forward and left vulnerable late. Much better draw this time and will give a sight. TIMELY NEEDS (5) was close to a win before a break with a couple of minors over further. Will stalk the lead here and finish yard. MISS STRAT (7) is a filly by Stratosphere out of Inoseyou making her first appearance. Among the placings in recent trial and Lauryn Bingley sticks with her. Can play a role. SORELL EAGLES (4) is a three-year-old gelding by Alpine Eagle from Sorell Miss making debut. Well educated and off the low draw worth keeping safe.",
